snippet.title: CATASS promotional video
snippet.description:
.

Download for free on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2430220/CATASS/

I'm currently working on a more stable release for Android. Sorry for the inconvenience.

Welcome to CATASS, a game where you are A CAT! Play as a sneaky feline on its personal quest. CATASS is an ad-free casual game with fun and challenging levels. Solve puzzles in and out of the game to unlock unique skins and obtain epic items. Complete all levels and become the supreme cat!

CATASS is a personal project developed solo to provide a fun and exciting experience.

Download CATASS now and experience the thrill of being a cat. You won't regret it!
